@startuml
hide footbox

skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #5a7088
skinparam SequenceLifeLineBorderColor #5a7088
skinparam SequenceLifeLineBackgroundColor #f7fbff
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #4d6a86
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #f7fbff
skinparam ParticipantFontColor #1f2f3d
skinparam NoteBorderColor #96a7b8
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #fffdf3

participant Primary as P
participant Secondary as S

== Local busy (frame pool low watermark) ==

P -> S: I-frame
P -> S: I-frame
P -> S: I-frame (P=1)
note right of S: pool → LOW_WATER\nlocal busy set

S --> P: RNR (F=1)
note left: TX I-frames suspended\nat Primary

... Primary polls periodically ...

P -> S: RR (P=1)
note right of S: application reading\nframes from pool
S --> P: RNR (F=1)
note left: still busy

P -> S: RR (P=1)
note right of S: pool → NORMAL\nlocal busy cleared
S --> P: RR (F=1)
note left: TX I-frames resumed

P -> S: I-frame
P -> S: I-frame

@enduml
